INSERT INTO armies (id, village_id, current_map_field_id, hero_id, units, smithy, tribe, player_id)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
                ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
                SET
                    units = $5,
                    hero_id = $4,
                    current_map_field_id = $3,
                    village_id = $2,
                    player_id = $8,
                    tribe = $7,
                    smithy = $6
